 Enable unsafe SwiftShader fallback seems to be the key switch

 chrome://flags/#enable-unsafe-swiftshader

 --enable-unsafe-swiftshader
  


[root@realoption ~]# google-chrome-stable --headless --no-sandbox --disable-gpu --disable-dev-shm-usage --window-size=1280,1024 --screenshot=screenshot1.png https://yahoo.com

you get screenshot1.png in your root directory

